SUMMARY:Portland Art Museum: Free First Thursday
DESCRIPTION:Category: Arts & Culture\nCost: $27.50 adults\; FREE First Thur
 sday\; $5 Oregon Trail Card (up to 2 tickets)\nInfo: Explore the museum's 
 diverse collections for free. Tickets can be reserved online one week in a
 dvance or at the door. Often includes live DJs\, guided tours\, and specia
 l programming. Part of Portland's First Thursday arts tradition.\nAddress:
  1219 SW Park Ave\, Portland\, OR 97205\nPhone: 503-226-2811\nWebsite: htt
 ps://portlandartmuseum.org/
LOCATION:1219 SW Park Ave\, Portland\, OR 97205
URL:https://portlandartmuseum.org/
RRULE:FREQ=MONTHLY;BYDAY=TH;BYSETPOS=1
CATEGORIES:Arts & Culture
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
